  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive buildable base ornament.<br>This elaborate, <span class=\"name name-stellar\">gold-fringed flag</span> features a rendition of the iconic Alpha Vector Starship. Plant in a habitable base to commemorate completion of the inaugural <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Expedition</span>, 'Pioneers'.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属可建造基地装饰。<br>这面华丽的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">金边旗</span>上绘制了标志性的 A 型制导飞船。将这面大旗立在宜居基地内，纪念你完成第一次<span class=\"name name-stellar\">远征</span>，“先驱”。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的可建造基地裝飾。<br>作工精緻的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">鑲金旗幟</span>，上面畫的是著名的「A 向量」太空船。將這支旗幟插在可居住的基地，紀念第一次完成<span class=\"name name-stellar\">探險</span>「先鋒」。"
  },
